57 to the Constitution of Alabama of 2022, to authorize the
58 full-time mayors of municipalities in the county to
59 participate in the Employees' Retirement System of Alabama
60 under the same terms and conditions as other employees in the
61 same retirement system.
62 Proposed by Act ____."
63 This description shall be followed by the following
64 language:
65 "Yes( ) No( )."
66 Section 3. The proposed amendment shall become valid as
67 part of the Constitution of Alabama of 2022, when approved by
68 a majority of the qualified electors voting thereon.
